## STEP 4: Create Jenkins Pipeline (Browser – Jenkins UI)

1. Open http://localhost:8080
2. Click "New Item"
3. Enter name → Select "Pipeline" → OK

---

## STEP 5: Connect GitHub Repository (Jenkins UI)

* Go to Pipeline section
* Select "Pipeline script from SCM"
* SCM: Git
* Repository URL: https://github.com/JeevanJeraldm/Devops-Lab.git
* Branch: main

---

## STEP 6: Add Docker Hub Credentials (Jenkins UI)

1. Go to "Manage Jenkins"
2. Click "Credentials"
3. Add Credentials:

   * Username: jeevanjeraldm
   * Password: Docker Hub password/token
   * ID: dockerhub-creds

